data.description: WOW!!!  Move right into your own private retreat!  Updated in 2021 and newer:  freshly painted, LIFE proof laminate flooring throughout, spectacular brand-new primary bathroom (vanity, ceramic flooring, floor to ceiling ceramic shower), stainless steel kitchen appliances, new roof, covered patio, private fenced yard for entertaining, has a shed (this is just the beginning of a list of updates).  There is 2nd floor laundry room and a great room (which is currently being used as an office.  The basement is partially finished. This lovely home is close to local amenities.  *Offer on property is subject to sale of buyers home.  Buyer has 24 hours to perform.  Please call listing agent for details.
